                                                         \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/2-file-save-as-option-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/2-file-save-as-option-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/2-file-save-as-option-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/2-file-save-as-option-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"836\" height=\"475\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Shows file save as option in Notepad on Windows\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/2-file-save-as-option-notepad-windows.png\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/2-file-save-as-option-notepad-windows.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Navigate to the directory you want to save the file, type a name, keep the file type as \u003cstrong\u003etxt\u003c/strong\u003e, and click \u003cstrong\u003eSave\u003c/strong\u003e. \n                                            \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"764\" height=\"596\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"saving Notepad LOG file as a txt file type\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/3-save-notepad-as-log-file.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Don’t type anything yet, and close out of Notepad.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Open the log file you saved to discover the current date and time listed at the top. The cursor automatically moves to the next line for your entry. Type in your first entry and press \u003cstrong\u003eCtrl + S\u003c/strong\u003e to save it. \n                                            \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"918\" height=\"307\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"typing data in a log journal in notepad in windows\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/4-typing-log-journal-notepad-windows.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Now comes the cool part. You can keep your log open during the day, and when you want to add something new, press \u003cstrong\u003eEnter\u003c/strong\u003e and then \u003cstrong\u003eF5\u003c/strong\u003e to add the current time and date to add a new entry. \n                                            \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"918\" height=\"343\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"press F5 for a new time and date entry for your log file in notepad\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/5-enter-f5-new-entry-time-date.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_6\"\u003e\n\n        \n            \u003cp\u003eYour logs will eventually become larger and more difficult to navigate. So, when you need to find something, press \u003cstrong\u003eCtrl + F\u003c/strong\u003e to bring up the search box and type in what you want to find.\u003c/p\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"a-time-stamped-log-in-notepad-on-your-pc-is-helpful\"\u003e\n                        A time-stamped log in Notepad on your PC is helpful\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you are a fan of using \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/spell-checker-tool-for-windows-11-notepad/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eNotepad on your Windows PC\u003c/a\u003e, this tip helps you keep track of your daily events by providing the exact time and date for each log entry. Even if you have been hesitant to work with Notepad, try this, and you might find that simplicity is better than working in more \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/create-and-use-digital-journal-in-notion/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ecomplex journaling apps\u003c/a\u003e like Notion or OneNote. Or, you can use it for specific events that don\u0026#39;t require all that.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eFor example, I use two to three logs daily, including ones for work and personal events. It\u0026#39;s a good solution for tracking financial transactions and bills. Of course, those companies provide time-dated receipts for payments. But having a backup log for your records or if systems go down is wise. You can also have your log file in a folder backed up to \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/microsoft-onedrive-making-easier-to-find-your-files/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eOneDrive\u003c/a\u003e or \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/onedrive-windows-pc-vs-google-drive/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGoogle Drive\u003c/a\u003e. When used right, a Notepad log file is an excellent way to keep track of your days and boost productivity. It\u0026#39;s a great option if you don’t need images and just want an easy-to-use text-based tracking solution.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n        \n\n    \n\n        \n\n\n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
